            "text": "Too Faced Shadow Insurance (Champagne)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I didn't spend much time on makeup on this trip, so "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://amzn.to/2jkXENC",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "this"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " was the perfect eye shadow. It is an eye shadow primer but the beautiful champagne color makes it a great shadow for an everyday, neutral look. Now that I'm home, I love using it as a base for other eye shadows."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "CoverGirl Outlast Stay Fabulous Foundation"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "em"
              }
            ],
            "text": "{Not pictured because it's very well-loved}"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I've used "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://amzn.to/2jjX5E9",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "this foundation"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (in shade 825) for a couple years now, and I still think it's the best. This was perfect for the trip since it has SPF 20 and stays on all day long - even through rainy and snowy days."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Anastasia Brow Wiz (Dark Brown)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://amzn.to/2jjX9nn",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "This"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " is another product I've used for a while, but I love it even more as a travel product. I can't go without filling in my eyebrows, and this is very easy to apply and lasts all day."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Nars Blush (Oasis)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I used "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://amzn.to/2jKnyXZ",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "this blush"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " every day. The light plum color was great for our mostly casual days, and easy to dress up a look with by applying a few more swipes."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "OPI Wipe-Off! Nail Polish Remover Wipes"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I did continue to paint my nails while traveling just because I bite my nails if I don't paint them. There was no way I was going to carry around a bottle of nail polish remover, so I ordered a few of the OPI polish remover packets. One of these nail polish remover packets takes off all of my nail polish and toe polish very quickly. I find it a lot less messy and less damaging to the nail than other regular nail polish remover bottles I have used."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Hair Products"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/2016-04-08-13.27.53-1024x768.jpg",
              "alt": "2016-04-08 13.27.53",
              "title": null
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I have naturally very thick and wavy hair. Usually I straighten my hair after letting it air dry over night, and then I don't have to wash or style my hair much for the next five or six days. Other days I just let my hair be naturally wavy, but I've never been very happy with that look. I knew I wouldn't take the time to straighten my hair much while we were gone, so I wanted to bring a couple products to help my naturally wavy hair stay in place while we were out and about."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Living Proof  Frizz Nourishing Styling Creme"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I'm not sure how it works, but somehow "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://amzn.to/2jRvOtx",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "this curl creme"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " helps my wavy hair stay in place much better than it does on its own. Since returning home, I have started wearing my hair wavy much more often just because of this product and how well it works in combination with the Ghost Oil I mention below."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Verb Ghost Oil"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I have found that adding just a little bit of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://amzn.to/2ipggfY",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "this oil"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " to my hair keeps the waves from getting as frizzy as they do naturally."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
